headline.main: RED FORCES FIRM; Reported Barring Way to Nazi Expedition Like That Against Crete

lead_paragraph: BERNE, Switzerland, Friday, Sept. 26 -- The long-expected German thrust in Crimea has been underway for more than twenty-four hours, it was acknowledged by the Russian spokesman in Moscow early today.
